Package stars

Class User_details

java.lang.Object
stars.User_details
All Implemented Interfaces:
FlatFileObject
public class User_details
extends java.lang.Object
implements FlatFileObject
A class that holds details regarding a user's account A user can be either a student or an admin. in the Stars system. Users are identified by their usernames, which must be unique.

2020/11/14
